{"tid":1862561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【守望相助】佐敦恆豐「Fresh Up」對面店主提供一小樽消毒水替其消毒","createTime":"2020-02-04T16:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:03:36.000Z","uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"53fb6e7abc9e9589d515342cd8a84db1a810ce33","tid":1862561,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"本港今日新增兩宗新型肺炎確診個案，其中一名 64 歲女病人，是佐敦恆豐中心一間服裝店「Fresh Up」的店主，發病後仍然有開店 4 日。在 Fresh up 對面鋪頭的店員張小姐指，最後一次見女病者是年三十晚，當時她看起來氣息正常，並無異樣；張小姐又指家人知道武漢肺炎患者的店舖，與她工作的店非常接近很擔心，而由於現時消毒用品供應緊張，僱主只能夠提供一小樽消毒水給她消毒店舖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2AnaVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2AnaVF.jpg&h=75c77243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2830155113736757/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2830155113736757%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=b8a89924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2830155113736757/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"b06901baaa2c715a87d352745804a58bf85367b9","tid":1862561,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f07fd737ed06237c8fc0f14ac0fb67ee3aa5aa3","tid":1862561,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"個c9幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaff58c6d7686196354ea01eb43ac1eebc5d03b7","tid":186